(thirdQuint)Value of Radiological Follow up in Children Hospitalized With Lobar Pneumonia.

 Thew study will include follow up data in a group of about 200 patients admitted with lobar pneumonia during the years 2006 to 2007.

 All the clinical and laboratory data will be collected and also the X rays findings.

 The findings of follow up X rays if they were performed will also be summarized.

